# ☕ Coffee Cart Automation Framework

This project is a Selenium + TestNG based automation framework designed to test the Coffee Cart web application. It uses the Page Object Model (POM), data-driven testing, and includes reusable utilities, listeners, and structured reporting.

---

## 📌 Features

- TestNG with suite-level control  
- Page Object Model (POM)  
- Data-driven tests via Excel  
- Centralized WebDriver management  
- ExtentReports / HTML test outputs  
- TestNG Listeners for custom logging  
- Maven for build and dependency management  

